All 3 tests pass. Here's the fix:

**In MSTest v4, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>` returns the typed value instead of using an `out` parameter.**

```csharp
// Before (v3) — causes CS1615 in v4
Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor, out var typed);

// After (v4) — return value instead of out param
var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor);
```

I also updated your package reference from `3.8.0` → `4.1.0` so the project builds and all 3 tests pass.
